<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: inline-block;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 72px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .redirect-button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none; /* Important for the anchor tag */
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .redirect-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>Oops! The resource you requested at **<%= url %>** could not be found.</p>
        <p>Don't worry, you can return to the main users list.</p>
        
        <a href="/users" class="redirect-button">Go to Users List</a>
        
    </div>
</body>
</html>